# Kids Food Fight — Project Rules

## Monorepo Layout
- `app/` — React Native (Expo) mobile app
- `frontend/` — Vite + React admin console (calls `/api/v1/admin/*`, superuser JWT)
- `backend/` — FastAPI + PostgreSQL API
- `docker-compose.yml` — **repository root**; Postgres + backend + frontend (nginx)
- `kff_prototype/` — Reference ONLY. Never copy code from here.

## Schema Design
- The database schema is being designed from scratch. Do not derive models from `kff_prototype`.
- All SQLAlchemy models live in `backend/app/models.py`.
- Pydantic schemas live in `backend/app/schemas.py`.

## API Conventions
- Base prefix: `/api/v1`
- Admin prefix: `/api/v1/admin` (requires active superuser JWT)
- Auth: JWT Bearer token
- Error shape: `{ "detail": "..." }` (FastAPI default)
- Pagination: `?skip=0&limit=20` on list endpoints

## Secrets
- Never commit `.env` files. Use `.env.example` with placeholder values only.
